---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services — Skief Labs" description="Data Intelligence and Sales Acceleration services for B2B companies. AI-powered outbound systems and automated data pipelines.">
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-36">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="heading-serif text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-navy-900 mb-8">
          Two services.<br />Both done seriously.
        </h1>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          <p>Skief Labs works on two specific problems for B2B companies: getting the right data, and building the outbound systems that turn it into pipeline.</p>
          <p>We don't offer a menu of services. We don't take on work outside these two areas.</p>
          <p>If either problem is real for your business, it's worth a conversation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-10">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book a 30-minute discovery call</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICE ONE: DATA INTELLIGENCE -->
  <section class="section-dark py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mb-16">
        <p class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-blue-500 mb-4">Service One</p>
        <h2 class="heading-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl text-linen mb-6">
          Data Intelligence
        </h2>
        <p class="text-linen/60 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl">
          The data your team needs — built, enriched, and delivered automatically.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- The Problem -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 mb-20">
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">
          <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-linen/50 mb-4">The Problem</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-4 text-linen/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>Most B2B teams have a data problem they've quietly learned to work around.</p>
          <p>Lists that are months out of date before they're used. Research that pulls senior people away from higher-value work. Enrichment that's incomplete, inconsistent, or both. Decisions made on inputs no one fully trusts.</p>
          <p>This isn't a tools problem. It's a systems problem.</p>
          <p>The fix isn't another data subscription. It's a pipeline that finds, enriches, scores, and delivers the right information automatically — so the work stops requiring people.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="separator !border-linen/10 mb-20" />

      <!-- What We Build -->
      <div class="mb-20">
        <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-linen/50 mb-10">What We Build</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
          <div class="border border-linen/10 rounded-lg p-8">
            <h4 class="text-linen text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Research & Scraping Pipelines</h4>
            <p class="text-linen/70 text-base leading-relaxed">
              The data your team currently sources by hand — contacts, companies, roles, signals — collected automatically from the sources that matter for your specific use case. Continuously refreshed, not exported once and forgotten.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-linen/10 rounded-lg p-8">
            <h4 class="text-linen text-lg font-semibold mb-3">AI-Powered Enrichment & Scoring</h4>
            <p class="text-linen/70 text-base leading-relaxed">
              Raw data isn't useful. We build enrichment logic that layers context, qualifies records, and scores outputs — so what reaches your team is clean, relevant, and ready to act on.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-linen/10 rounded-lg p-8">
            <h4 class="text-linen text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Agentic Research Workflows</h4>
            <p class="text-linen/70 text-base leading-relaxed">
              For complex research that currently consumes senior time, we build AI agents that gather, structure, and summarize — in the exact format your team uses to make decisions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-linen/10 rounded-lg p-8">
            <h4 class="text-linen text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Signal & Trigger Identification</h4>
            <p class="text-linen/70 text-base leading-relaxed">
              Hiring activity. Funding events. Technology changes. Leadership moves. We surface the buying signals relevant to your ICP automatically, so your team acts on fresh intelligence instead of stale assumptions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="separator !border-linen/10 mb-20" />

      <!-- Who This Is For -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 mb-20">
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">
          <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-linen/50 mb-4">Who This Is For</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-4 text-linen/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>Data Intelligence engagements serve teams where the quality of inputs directly determines the quality of everything downstream.</p>
          <p>Marketing teams using data for account targeting, segmentation, and campaign intelligence.</p>
          <p>HR and talent teams using it for candidate sourcing, market mapping, and competitive research.</p>
          <p>Growth teams using it to feed sales systems with reliable, continuously refreshed data.</p>
          <p class="text-linen/50">This is not a fit if you need a quick list or a one-time export. This is for teams with a recurring data need that has outgrown what manual effort or off-the-shelf tools can sustain.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="separator !border-linen/10 mb-20" />

      <!-- What Good Looks Like + Engagement -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 mb-12">
        <div>
          <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-linen/50 mb-6">What Good Looks Like</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-linen/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            <p>When a Data Intelligence system is working, your team stops talking about data quality.</p>
            <p>They trust the inputs. Decisions get faster. The research backlog disappears. The people who used to spend hours finding information spend that time using it instead.</p>
            <p class="text-linen font-semibold">Teams typically reduce manual data handling by 80–90%.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-linen/50 mb-6">How This Engagement Works</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-linen/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            <p>Every Data Intelligence engagement starts with the discovery call. From there, we scope the work properly before anything is built.</p>
            <p>We build to a fixed scope with full documentation and handoff at the end.</p>
            <p>Some clients extend into an ongoing arrangement where we continue running and refreshing the system. Others take it and run it themselves. Either way, you own it completely.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-linen text-lg font-semibold mb-6">System builds from $5,000.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book a 30-minute discovery call</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICE TWO: SALES ACCELERATION -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mb-16">
        <p class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-blue-500 mb-4">Service Two</p>
        <h2 class="heading-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl text-navy-900 mb-6">
          Sales Acceleration
        </h2>
        <p class="text-navy-900/60 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl">
          More pipeline. Without more headcount.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- The Problem -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 mb-20">
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">
          <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-navy-900/40 mb-4">The Problem</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>Most B2B outbound fails for a reason that has nothing to do with the product, the market, or the team.</p>
          <p>It fails because the system underneath is fragile.</p>
          <p>Manual list building. Inconsistent personalization. Follow-up that depends on someone remembering. No visibility into what's working until it's too late to fix it.</p>
          <p>The result is a lot of effort producing unpredictable results — and a team that's busy but not productive.</p>
          <p class="text-navy-900 font-semibold">We fix the system. Then we run it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="separator mb-20" />

      <!-- What We Do -->
      <div class="mb-20">
        <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-navy-900/40 mb-10">What We Do</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-900/5">
            <h4 class="text-navy-900 text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Outbound System Design</h4>
            <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-base leading-relaxed">
              Before a single message is sent, we design the full targeting logic, data sources, personalization framework, and sequence architecture.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-900/5">
            <h4 class="text-navy-900 text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Clay-Powered Targeting & Enrichment</h4>
            <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-base leading-relaxed">
              We use Clay as the data backbone — building dynamic lead sources, enrichment waterfalls, and scoring logic that ensures every contact your team reaches is the right one.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-900/5">
            <h4 class="text-navy-900 text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Multi-Channel Sequence Execution</h4>
            <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-base leading-relaxed">
              Email and LinkedIn, working together. Touchpoints designed around actual buyer behavior and intent signals — not generic cadences copied from a playbook.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-900/5">
            <h4 class="text-navy-900 text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Done-For-You Operation</h4>
            <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-base leading-relaxed">
              We run the outbound. Research, enrichment, personalization, sequencing, inbox management, and continuous optimization — handled by us. Your team focuses on the conversations.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="separator mb-20" />

      <!-- Who This Is For -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 mb-20">
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">
          <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-navy-900/40 mb-4">Who This Is For</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>Sales Acceleration is built for B2B founders, sales leaders, and growth teams who know their outbound should be working harder — and who are honest about the fact that the current approach isn't scaling.</p>
          <p class="text-navy-900/50">This is not a fit for teams looking for a short campaign or a quick blast. This is for teams who want a reliable outbound motion they can build on.</p>
          <p>We work with a small number of Sales Acceleration clients at a time. That's not a positioning line — it's how we maintain the quality that makes the work effective.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="separator mb-20" />

      <!-- What Good Looks Like + Engagement -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 mb-12">
        <div>
          <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-navy-900/40 mb-6">What Good Looks Like</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            <p>When Sales Acceleration is running well, outbound stops feeling like a gamble.</p>
            <p>Your team has consistent conversations in the calendar. The pipeline becomes predictable. The manual research and personalization that used to take hours happens automatically.</p>
            <p class="text-navy-900 font-semibold">Most clients see 3–5x more outreach capacity with the same headcount, and a 40–60% reduction in time spent on manual prospecting.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-navy-900/40 mb-6">How This Engagement Works</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            <p>Sales Acceleration begins with a pilot project — a defined scope, fixed price, and clear deliverable.</p>
            <p>The pilot covers ICP definition, data sourcing and enrichment via Clay, sequence architecture and copy, system build and launch, and first weeks of live execution.</p>
            <p>Most clients move to an ongoing monthly retainer after the pilot. There is no obligation to continue beyond the pilot.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-navy-900 text-lg font-semibold mb-6">Pilot projects from $10,000. Ongoing retainer from $3,000/month.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book a 30-minute discovery call</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- A NOTE ON AI -->
  <section class="section-dark py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="heading-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-linen mb-8">
          A note on AI & automation
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-linen/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>You'll notice we don't list AI and automation as a service.</p>
          <p>That's intentional.</p>
          <p>AI and automation are how we build — not what we sell. Every Data Intelligence pipeline runs on automation. Every Sales Acceleration system uses AI for enrichment, personalization, and research at scale.</p>
          <p>We don't offer automation as a standalone product because the technology is never the point. The point is the outcome — cleaner data, more pipeline, less friction for the people doing the work.</p>
          <p>If you're looking for a partner who uses automation and AI seriously — embedded in systems designed to solve real problems — we might be exactly right.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE DON'T DO -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="heading-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-navy-900 mb-8">
          What we don't do
        </h2>
        <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We think clarity here saves everyone time.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-navy-900/70 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <li>We don't run one-off campaigns.</li>
          <li>We don't take on projects where we're one of several vendors being evaluated.</li>
          <li>We don't offer free audits or speculative work.</li>
          <li>We don't build systems that require us to stay involved forever.</li>
          <li>We don't work with teams who want speed over substance.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-navy-900/50 text-base mt-6">
          These aren't restrictions designed to sound exclusive. They're the conditions under which our work is actually good.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-linen pb-24 md:pb-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book a 30-minute discovery call</a>
      <p class="text-navy-900/50 text-sm mt-3 italic">No pitch. No obligation. Just clarity.</p>
      <p class="text-navy-900/40 text-sm mt-8 italic font-serif">More business. Less busyness.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
